INSERT INTO subscriptions (user_id, plan_id, status, start_date, end_date, auto_renew, created_at, updated_at)
VALUES (
  1,
  5,
  'active',
  NOW(),
  '2099-12-31 23:59:59',
  0,
  NOW(),
  NOW()
)
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE
  plan_id = 5,
  status = 'active',
  end_date = '2099-12-31 23:59:59',
  updated_at = NOW();
